== 开发和制作 ==
2012年9月5日报道说J·J·艾布拉姆斯和J·H·威曼开发一部类似[[危机边缘|危机边缘]]的电视剧，该剧设定在不久的未来人工智能的发展的及其成熟，一批人形机器警察和真人警察组成搭档<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/09/jj-abramsj-h-wyman-drama-lands-at-fox-with-pilot-production-commitment/ |title=J.J. Abrams/J.H. Wyman Drama Lands At Fox With Pilot Production Commitment |access-date=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2013-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015084629/http://www.deadline.com/2012/09/jj-abramsj-h-wyman-drama-lands-at-fox-with-pilot-production-commitment/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvfantasy.net/2012/09/07/shows-in-development-2012-09-07/ |title=9月7日新剧开发消息 |access-date=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2016-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403120317/http://tvfantasy.net/2012/09/07/shows-in-development-2012-09-07/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年1月25日FOX宣布拍摄本剧的[[电视试播|试映集]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/01/jj-abramsjh-wymans-drama-gets-pilot-order-at-fox/ |title=J.J. Abrams/J.H. Wyman’s Futuristic Cop Drama Gets Pilot Order At Fox |access-date=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2013-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015080004/http://www.deadline.com/2013/01/jj-abramsjh-wymans-drama-gets-pilot-order-at-fox/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvfantasy.net/2013/01/26/shows-in-development-2013-01-26/ |title=1月26日新剧开发及剧集变动消息 |access-date=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2019-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725095752/http://tvfantasy.net/2013/01/26/shows-in-development-2013-01-26/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，试播集将由[[布拉德·安德森|布拉德·安德森]]执导<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/02/jason-moore-brad-anderson-fred-savage-david-wain-tommy-schlamme-direct-pilots/ |title=Jason Moore, Brad Anderson, Fred Savage, David Wain, Tommy Schlamme Direct Pilots |access-date=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2013-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130316065709/http://www.deadline.com/2013/02/jason-moore-brad-anderson-fred-savage-david-wain-tommy-schlamme-direct-pilots/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Mekia Cox将客串试播集饰演约翰·肯尼士的前女友<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/s-epatha-merkerson-jeffrey-ross-melinda-mcgraw-among-pilot-guest-castings/ |title=S. Epatha Merkerson, Jeffrey Ross, Melinda McGraw Among Pilot Guest Castings |access-date=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413002427/http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/s-epatha-merkerson-jeffrey-ross-melinda-mcgraw-among-pilot-guest-castings/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；该片开发过程中名字曾经用过《Human》<ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/03/20/development-update-wednesday-march-20-501514/10255/ Development Update: Wednesday, March 20]</ref>。

2013年5月8日FOX宣布预定本剧于[[2013年－2014年美国电视网节目表|2013年－2014年]]播出，并确认了该剧的名称为《Almost Human》<ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/05/08/development-update-wednesday-may-8-fox-drama-series-pick-ups-981510/10326/ Development Update: Wednesday, May 8 - FOX Drama Series Pick Ups Read more at http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/05/08/development-update-wednesday-may-8-fox-drama-series-pick-ups-981510/10326/#puAX6ekqieWKZcb9.99]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvfantasy.net/2013/05/10/fox-ordered-five-comedy-four-drama-and-more-updated/ |title=Fox提前预订五部情景喜剧和四部故事剧、NBC情况逐渐明朗及其他消息 (已更新) |access-date=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2016-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160407094032/http://tvfantasy.net/2013/05/10/fox-ordered-five-comedy-four-drama-and-more-updated/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在5月13日公布的时间表中该剧将于秋季晚些时候于周一晚8点播出，之前播出一段时间的[[识骨寻踪|识骨寻踪]]将让出档期<ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/05/13/fox-announces-primetime-slate-for-2013-2014-season-254005/20130513fox01/ FOX Announces Primetime Slate for 2013-2014 Season]</ref>，6月26日表示该剧将于11月4日开播<ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/06/26/fox-announces-fall-premiere-dates-for-the-2013-2014-season-545310/20130626fox01/ FOX Announces Fall Premiere Dates for the 2013-2014 Season]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvfantasy.net/2013/06/27/fox-fall-premiere-dates/ |title=Fox公布秋季节目首播时间表 |access-date=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2016-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406112209/http://tvfantasy.net/2013/06/27/fox-fall-premiere-dates/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

该片的开发者J·H·威曼表示该剧相对于[[危机边缘|危机边缘]]更为大众化是标准的警匪剧，另外剧组会尝试像危机边缘那样保留主线故事<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvfantasy.net/2013/06/29/newsletter-2013-06-29-under-the-dome-tvd-almost-human-glee-revolution-got-and-more/ |title=6月29日简讯：苍穹下、吸血鬼日记、机器之心、欢乐合唱团、革命、权力的游戏及其他 |access-date=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2016-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404160348/http://tvfantasy.net/2013/06/29/newsletter-2013-06-29-under-the-dome-tvd-almost-human-glee-revolution-got-and-more/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
